		"description": {
			"value": "<p><strong>Buff</strong></p><ul><li><p>When you take a Action to toss an <em>Ioun Stone</em> into the air, the stone orbits your head at a distance of [[/r 1d3]] feet, conferring its benefit to you while doing so. You can have up to three <em>Ioun Stones</em> orbiting your head at the same time.</p></li><li><p>As a Action, you can seize and stow any number of <em>Ioun Stones</em> orbiting your head. If your Attunement to an <em>Ioun Stone</em> ends while it's orbiting your head, the stone falls as though you had dropped it.</p></li><li><p>Your &amp;reference[Wisdom] increases by 2, to a maximum of 20, while this incandescent blue sphere orbits your head.</p></li></ul>",
			"chat": ""
		},
